text: Daniel Boone Arboretum is an arboretum located along a portion of the Daniel Boone Greenway in Harrogate, Tennessee. The arboretum contains over 50 labeled species of native trees. ==See also== * Daniel Boone Native Gardens (Boone, North Carolina) * List of botanical gardens in the United States Category:Arboreta in Tennessee Category:Botanical gardens in Tennessee Category:Protected areas of Claiborne County, Tennessee Category:Harrogate, Tennessee
title: Daniel Boone Arboretum
